    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let’s get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, pat dry with kitchen paper and roughly chop</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>into 2 wedges per person</p>",
