    {
      "instruction": "<p>While your rice is cooking, remove the skin from your <strong>smoked mackerel fillet[s] </strong>and discard</p><p>Tear the <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>mackerel </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
